# GET /

### root returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/

### root has expected fields (total_nodes, top_level_categories, leaf_nodes, max_depth, categories_by_level)
GET http://localhost:8000/

### root node counts (394 total, 11 top-level, 341 leaves, depth 4)
GET http://localhost:8000/

### root categories_by_level covers all nodes
GET http://localhost:8000/


# GET /categories

### categories returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/categories

### categories returns 11 entries
GET http://localhost:8000/categories

### categories contains User Interface Errors
GET http://localhost:8000/categories

### categories each have required fields (id, name, level, children)
GET http://localhost:8000/categories

### categories are all level 1
GET http://localhost:8000/categories


# GET /categories/{id}

### category by ID returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/user-interface-errors

### category by ID returns correct name
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/user-interface-errors

### category by ID includes children (Functionality, Communication)
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/user-interface-errors

### category by ID has empty breadcrumb for root
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/user-interface-errors

### category unknown ID returns 404
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/does-not-exist


# GET /categories/{id}/subtree

### subtree returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/error-handling/subtree

### subtree children are nested objects
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/error-handling/subtree

### subtree unknown ID returns 404
GET http://localhost:8000/categories/does-not-exist/subtree


# GET /nodes

### nodes returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes

### nodes returns all 394
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes

### nodes filter level 1 matches categories (11 results)
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes?level=1

### nodes filter level 4 returns deepest nodes
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes?level=4

### nodes filter parent_id
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes?parent_id=user-interface-errors

### nodes leaves only (341 results, child_count 0)
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes?leaves_only=true

### nodes invalid level returns 422
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes?level=5


# GET /nodes/{id}

### node by ID returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes/spelling-errors

### node by ID has description
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes/spelling-errors

### node by ID breadcrumb lists ancestors (User Interface Errors, Communication)
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes/spelling-errors

### node unknown ID returns 404
GET http://localhost:8000/nodes/no-such-node


# GET /search

### search returns 200
GET http://localhost:8000/search?q=boundary

### search results contain query term
GET http://localhost:8000/search?q=overflow

### search results include breadcrumb
GET http://localhost:8000/search?q=cursor

### search no match returns empty list
GET http://localhost:8000/search?q=xyzzyplugh

### search query too short returns 422
GET http://localhost:8000/search?q=x

### search missing query returns 422
GET http://localhost:8000/search
